{"tid":376642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洪水獲救　川肥豬露出神秘笑容","createTime":"2017-08-27T06:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T16:40:00.000Z","uid":732,"like":643,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"427cb89b308bcc56c4c82f7be6248d8d8bd6088a","tid":376642,"uid":732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/794499/xlarge/de63443312c2b834b44292baafd89afb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F794499%2Fxlarge%2Fde63443312c2b834b44292baafd89afb.jpg&h=930fbac1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日前，四川宜賓遭遇洪水，當地一隻肥豬被村民救出時，竟露出神秘笑容。<br />\n<br />\n據內媒報道，25日，四川宜賓橫江鎮因洪水來襲，村民緊急轉移重要物資，包括飼養的豬隻。不過，由於豬隻太重，需多名村民一齊幫忙，轉移過程困難重重。其中，一隻豬被兩名救援人員從房屋救出時，竟面帶神秘笑容。"},{"pid":"376be7d0c1c1ffe837c4b1f975dc79937c9c2878","tid":376642,"uid":34023,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:53:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e165ea8ddc7f470414060566b1cc66d64945b8a","tid":376642,"uid":45232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427b7d5e259fa77be4d7c54295110f58bc3c4fff","tid":376642,"uid":38516,"like":130,"dislike":4,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:54:23.000Z","msg":"好cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ecf544420b4bf01bbf23dd14b7e2dd78abd9d7e","tid":376642,"uid":82816,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:55:43.000Z","msg":"二師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3efb9b4fcbb8163a4eb6a0a1e128d55640a81eb","tid":376642,"uid":42374,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:56:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces